In Finnish:
Joulu versio aijemmastani CS:S mapista. Pieniä muutoksia ja lisäyksiä.

In English:
This is a holiday version of my previous CS:S map de_saunatupa, with small additions and changes.

in English:
de_saunatupa is a one bombsite map that is partially based on a popular map layout "rantasauna". Most of these maps in CS:S had many problems and missing details, such as lighting. So I wanted to make my version out of the layout. I made this map completely from a new file and built it from my memory, while making some additions and differences. The map has 14 playerstarts per team, cubemaps(reflections), soundscapes and a 3D skybox.

in Finnish:
de_saunatupa on perus saunamappi, joka perustuu osittain suositun rantasauna mapin pohjaan. Näitä mappeja on kuitenkin CS Sourcessa monta erilaista, eikä yhtä kunnollista porttia alkuperäisesta CS 1.6 mapista, joten tein mapin osittain muistista ja omilla ideoilla.

Hey ! I'm back with new sauna map ! It's been ages since I published a map but here's the new saunataikuri ! Some people may ask why its v3 since there's no v2 in banana , but there's simple explanation ;  I haven't published v2 but I will in future. I thought that v2 will be the last version but this map has turned into trilogy and hopefully this final version is the best of all

New features : 

1# More outdoor action.
2# You can climb on the roof. YAY !
3# I made just one bombsite for reason that two sites don't fit in saunamaps. But that's only my opinion and it still has balanced gameplay
4# And last but not least there's 4 secrets to find !

Pleaaaaaase leave a comment and rate of course !
Thanks and cya in the future ! (hopefully)

Mean terrorists have decided to blow up convenient resort. Terrorist are gonna blow up nice small restaurant at the pool area or the sauna. CTs have to stop terrorists and defend the resort for last man.

Mmmm yeah , This map was in fact a New Year project that delayed. I started in November but I took little break which delayed and delayed. If I'm honest , I bought CoD4 and started to play that D: and later MW2. Yeah but I tried to make this map balanced and fun to play , there's 5-6 secrets(not so sure xD) to find but please don't use noclip C; One secret is code locked door in the middle of map. I have hidden 6 numbers in the map and 2 numbers are wrong. You can only try 4 times / round to open door ,and if 4th time is failed , the door jams and you can try out on next round. And..... mm I'm not gonna tell you all :O It's up to you to find those secrets , Good luck

MAP BRIEFING

The terrorists have targetted a famous resort in Finland and have decided to make their action as the sun starts to set and place starts to close. While terrorists were waiting in their vans, local over heard the terrorists plan and reports this to the police and as the terrorists start to move, they're waiting, but the terrorists aren't unarmed.

OBJECTIVE
Terrorists: Plant the bomb on "sauna", area (A) on the map (Screenshot E) and Demolish the nice vacation resort along with its residents.
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map contains: "UFO, NPC, finnish flag, statues, secret areas etc.."
Recommented players/Max players: 20/64
Map contains a single bomb site.
Spawnpoints: Terrorists spawn from the garage near vans, from there they have 3 main ways to the bomb zone. Counter terrorists spawn from lobby close to the bomb zone.
All of the map, isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!

DE_sand_blast_beta_6 this will be the final beta version so the next one released will be the final one. please let me know if you find any issues or any suggestions for changes . I reccomend having fast downloading set up if you are putting this on a server its about a 10 - 20 minute download with out it. changes since B3 - i added a new walk way - i removed a walkway - added a bit more to some of the surrounding buildings - better optimization (better fps) - added more detail - changed bomb site B - added some more props - removed some props - removed some trees - made game play more even - added some double doors - swapped a wall with some rocks near bomb site B - removed the water in ct spawn - made the breakable wall in bomb site a better - removed the displacements from the middle market area - broke up the straight line from t spawn through the market a little bit - fixed some displacements - i removed the displacement from t spawn - made the walk way from t spawn to bomb site A wider - i brightened bomb site B - removed the displacements near bomb site B - changed a bunch of props - i have changed bomb site A a lot - added smoke effect to the sky - i have changed and added to ct spawn - fixed places where you could jump out of the map - fixed some places so you cannot jump onto props - made it harder to throw grenades into bomb site A - i have removed the background sounds - opened some areas up for more room to move around Known problems - the displacement in t spawn is black and weird in one area map build by Mastergun displacements by wiked sick skybox texture by karatekafer nav file and radar overview coming with the final version

De_Sandstorm - Bomb-Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists
from bombing target areas.

Team members must defuse any bombs 
that threaten targeted areas.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the
C4 must destroy one of the target areas. 

Other Notes: There are 2 bomb sites.

a Counter-Strike: Source experience by DocRock

Map Name: de_Sandstorm.bsp
Filesize:  9.7 mb un-zipped
Author:   DocRock
email:     docrock10@cox.net

==========================================
LEVEL DESCRIPTION: 

A sandstorm is slowing enveloping a small battle-worn town.  The townspeople are very proud of the town's Egyptian heritage.  There is great history here.  

The people work very hard to keep the town's structure solid, even though they realize their demise is soon - whether it be from the impending doom of the slowly moving sanddune, or the unending war which damages the city streets.  
                                          

Terrorists are an evil kind, and willingly destroy sections of the town, even bomb limestone blocks that the city dwellers 
use to try to rebuild their homes and walls.

==========================================

Special Map Note:  qUiCkSiLvEr spent many hours preparing the NAV file for this map, and re-textured the clouds so they would look like sand blowing across the sky. He also spent a great deal of time working the sounds through the map.  His work is, as always, superb, and I want to thank him for all he did for the success of this map.
